{
  "stem": "2522.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was quite clear, after the Russian advance started, after Stalingrad and started moving west-- it was quite clear by the early of 1944 that it was just a question of time when Germany will collapse.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so in 1944, the underground-- and there were two undergrounds.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a western underground and there was a communist underground run from Moscow-- one from London, one from Moscow-- started planning a way of bailing out out of the-- out of the Nazi dominance and finding some way of letting the Soviet army sweep west without destroying everything.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And of course, one of the issues my father had-- well, when the war really comes in, they will kill all the Jews regardless whether they are Lutheran or not anyway.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, then perhaps you will get killed not because you're a Jew but because the civilian population took enormous casualties.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was a plan which was largely launched by and supported by OSS.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were some OSS agents who started dropping in in early in 1944.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father, who controlled much of the food business was party to a major move to move stocks, stocks, food stocks into the mountain, you know, under the notion that there are some, some stores out there that really need lots of inventory because you know, the roads are muddy and, you know, and God knows what.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, absolutely not.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Absolutely didn't not know what he was doing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, he knew what he was doing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, he was-- well, he was a reserve officer of the Czechoslovak army.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, he was in uniform when we mobilized at the time of Munich.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Wait a minute.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Czechoslovakia mobilized in the time of Munich.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was ready to go and fight.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
